Watch podcasters and fans battle it out over geek culture touchstones in a "Geektastic Cage Match" at Wizard World Comic Con June 13, 2015, in Des Moines.

Want more Comic Con coverage? Check out our Ultimate guide to Wizard World Comic Conwhere you will find stories, interviews with headliners, photos, videos, and more from the Register's coverage of the event.
